creating JAR files

    // creates a JAR containing the files in the current directory
    jar -cvf Zoo.jar .
    jar --create --verbose --file Zoo.jar .

    // specifies directory
    jar -cvf Zoo.jar -C ch_01/welcome_to_java .

-c or --create      creates a new JAR file
-v or --verbose     prints details when working with JAR files
-f or --file        JAR filename
-C                  directory containing files to be used to create the JAR